tafsir[21]{c,v,t}:
  77,20,"Mbela Min tagaani mon- onon aade en-ummaade e ndiyam kouɗam ko ɗaam woni toɓɓere maniyyu."
  77,21,"Min mbaɗi ndiyam ɗam e nokku deenaaɗo ko oon woni rannga debba."
  77,22,"Haa e dumunna ganndaaɗo ko oon woni yonto caawgol suko."
  77,24,"Halkaare e lepte e perte woodanii wonande ɓeen fennooɓe baawal Alla."
  77,25,"Mbela Min mbaɗaani leydi ndi na sooma aade en fof."
  77,26,"Hondi renndini wonɓe heen wuurɓe e maayɓe ubbaaɓe e hendi ."
  77,28,"Halkaare e lepte woodanii wonande ɓeen fennooɓe njoɓdi mum en ñande ñalngu jnobdi."
  77,29,"Wiyanee fennooɓe ko nelaaɓe ngaddi ko- onon fennoobe- kuuƴe faade ko pennatnaɗon ko e lepte."
  77,30,"Njahee faade e mbeelu cuurki yiit mbanndi cate tate."
  77,33,"Peete werleteeɗe Alla noɗe ɓalwiri e noɗe mawniri a sikkat koɗe geloobi ɓaleeji."
  77,34,"Halkaare woodanii wonande ɓeen fennooɓe njoɓdi mum en ñande ñalngu jnobdi."
  77,35,"E o ñalngu ɓe kaalatah hay huunde."
  77,37,"Halkaare e perte woodanii ɓeen fennooɓe kabaruuji ñalngu jnobdi."
  77,39,"Si tawii hoɗon ndañi feere nde puuntiraton haa ndaɗon e lepte Alla pewjanee lan."
  77,40,"Halkaare woodanii wonande ɓeen fennooɓe njoɓdi mum en ñande ñalngu jnoɓdi."
  77,42,"E ɓesnaaɗe ɗeɓe tuuyate ñaamde."
  77,45,"Halkaare e lepte e perte woodanii ɓeen fennooɓe ko Alla heblani hulɓe e jnoɓdi."
  77,47,"Halkaare woodanii wonande ɓeen fennooɓe njoɓdi mum en ñande ñalngu jnoɓdi."
  77,48,"Si ɓee fennooɓe mbiyaama: njuule ngam Alla ɓe njuulatah."
  77,49,"Halkaare e lepte e perte e oon ñalawma woodanii fennuɓe ko nelaaɓe ngaddi ko ummaade ka Alla."
  77,50,"Siɓe goonɗinaani oo Quraana tellinaaɗo ummaade ka Alla honde yeewtere woɗnde ɓe goonɗinta?."